            <title>[SOLR-16867] Coordinator node role fails to create synthetic cores for multiple coordinator nodes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-16867</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the coordinator node role has a bug where multiple coordinator nodes that receive calls for the same configuration can hit a recursive loop and fail to create the necessary synthetic cores used to proxy calls.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This only occurs when there is &amp;gt;1 coordinator nodes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
